{"tid":241134,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【私樓控必睇．1】新界東北「隱世秘境」 臨海公屋走丹麥風","createTime":"2017-05-13T02:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T05:45:23.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a072a4b934f2032c9adee9ed8047e1788b17c74","tid":241134,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"如果閣下終日尋尋覓覓，尋找隱世IG拉絲打卡秘景，今日蘋果財經幫到你！是日介紹位於新界東北、深圳河以南的「隱世公屋」－－沙頭角迎海樓。<br />\n<br />\n前臨「極邪惡」180度無敵海景，沙頭角海壯麗景色一覽無遺，粉色油漆的外牆，油出一陣充滿少女味的丹麥小屋風格，你沒有看錯，的確，迎海樓是一座房協公屋。<br />\n<br />\n當市區樓怪則、屏風、1梯34伙橫行無忌之時；迎海樓安然地望著海，施施然劃成140個單位，樓高5層，極低密度。當市區業主為間百多呎劏房單位，捱生捱死做樓奴時；迎海樓的租戶，最細單位都有220呎，大單位約360呎。沒有極邪惡發水窗台，租戶仍然活得鬆動。<br />\n<br />\n沙頭角區民沈先生，原本租住位於香港保存最完整的民初建築群，有「民初街」之稱的新樓街單位。月租雖只需約2000元，但稱得上「民初街」，樓齡都有百年歷史。由入紙上樓之今，共花了15年時間的等待，終於抽到迎海樓大單位，「開心呀，要裝修到好靚，油油油咗十幾次。最少都十幾萬啦，好多自己做。」覺得自己幸運嗎？「好多人都好好彩，我係其中一個。」<br />\n<br />\n旁人看來，沈先生的確非常幸運，幸運在當距迎海樓3分鐘腳程的新盤「尚澄」，呎價逾萬元，最貴更達16,212元時；沈先生的單位，享同一個海景景緻，月租只要1988至3253元，假設住30年，租金120萬元有找。<br />\n<br />\n不過，要做幸運的公屋居民，首先，你要是沙頭角禁區居民；即是首先，要願意住山旯旮沙頭角；然後又首先，你接受到出入市區最少一小時車程；首先再首先，你又要接受一系列限制&hellip;&hellip;想知更多，且看下一則新聞。<br />\n<br />\n旁白：黎少凡、倪做慧<br />\n記者：倪做慧<br />\n攝影：馮鋒、陳家文<br />\n編導、剪接：陳家文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85784PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85784PM.jpg&h=84ad71bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙頭角公屋迎海樓，前臨「極邪惡」180度無敵海景。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/100550_fe31fad9b5709b2fbb701d5c838f13fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F100550_fe31fad9b5709b2fbb701d5c838f13fd.jpg&h=26fdff9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉色油漆的外牆，油出一陣充滿少女味的丹麥小屋風格。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/100631_02da9f35ae6e25fe3b928f4b3cf40041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F100631_02da9f35ae6e25fe3b928f4b3cf40041.jpg&h=95a04308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公屋住戶都享有靚海景。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xAK69T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xAK69T.jpg&h=8ee108cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公屋走廊闊落通爽。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18i56k3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18i56k3.jpg&h=62422707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n距迎海樓3分鐘腳程的新盤「尚澄」，呎價逾萬元。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685410&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685410%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=cd4d804c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685410%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&h=1018cbfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685410&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513</a>"},{"pid":"bf6006489e706f0f5f9ecc460f6b1f3e64448e59","tid":241134,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"【私樓控必睇．2】走入沙頭角禁地！居民：呢度天怒人怨<br />\n<br />\n「嗌交嗌到拍枱拍凳，同啲幫辦嗌。」「好似我哋讀書學過一句說話，朝令夕改」。於禁區經營茶餐廳的黃先生，他家族幾代人，都以沙頭角禁區為家，提到「禁區紙」問題，他談得激動。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，沙頭角禁區，沒錯是景色怡人，環境一流，但一張「禁區紙」卻為生活增添不少麻煩。他指，警方不時更改「禁區條例」，以「居民住戶證」可擔保禁區訪客數目為例，就時有改變，「我試過咁樣俾幫辦問，點解你啲朋友要入嚟沙頭角，我唔識答佢啊，點解呀？因為我啲朋友要上嚟探我囉！」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「喺上水禁區紙辦事處嗰度坐兩、三日，一定大把Argue。」他反問，「我哋禁區居民，都係香港人，點解對我哋限制越來越多。」<br />\n<br />\n自從2012年起，港府分三階段開放禁區，禁區範圍越縮越細，只剩沙頭角村、沙頭角墟及鄰近的中英街一帶，令禁區內店舖生意越使越差，黃先生慨嘆，「依家生意，唔係話賺錢，三幾千蚊生意維持得到嘅，當係生活一部分。我原本兩間舖頭嘅，做做下依家做淨一間。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到有否考慮過買入新盤尚澄，他表示本來考慮買，但開價太貴，「供唔到，依家講緊嘅係200幾萬兩百幾呎喎，係一個唔正常嘅單位喎。」他又指，尚澄每呎樓面地價只是1,104元，但開價逾萬元一呎實在不合理。<br />\n<br />\n生於斯、長於斯，黃先生繼續留在沙頭角，是因為這裡始終是他的家，「呢度簡單，人情味重啲，來來去去都係呢一班人，好似你哋嚟到我哋都好開心架，有多幾個人望下，開心架。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否建議區外人搬入，他表示，「退休啦，環境係好架。」<br />\n<br />\n旁白：黎少凡、倪做慧<br />\n記者：倪做慧<br />\n攝影：馮鋒、陳家文<br />\n編導、剪接：陳家文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/101015_7c39ebaa3f19556eaf5bfc97a60b7fd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F101015_7c39ebaa3f19556eaf5bfc97a60b7fd8.jpg&h=b84b4369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙頭角新公屋迎海樓。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHN4izz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHN4izz.jpg&h=8e40a083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙頭角有一間沒有開門的屈臣氏。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/101131_6095db4427c6edcb8544387faf989ae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F101131_6095db4427c6edcb8544387faf989ae7.jpg&h=4032bed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禁區內有街市，但無菜賣。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKQq6JS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKQq6JS.jpg&h=5fa85c69&s={SIZE}\" />・<br />\n車輛出入禁區都要經過檢查站。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/101252_d9826fdf2d21d4446aecc9a1639ccc5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F101252_d9826fdf2d21d4446aecc9a1639ccc5e.jpg&h=6913e22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港保存最完整的民初建築群，有「民初街」之稱的新樓街。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685893&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685893%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3ee56a82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685893%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&h=4e56a5c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685893&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513</a>"},{"pid":"6bd0411a66c412326483bc381e0e9356d823389b","tid":241134,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"沙頭角d公屋都唔太關市區人事 d樓都係派返畀沙頭角人都唔夠派"},{"pid":"9301474b7698448c1be525f8ecc12c6bc7103ef9","tid":241134,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"【私樓控必睇．3】蘋果VR 360直擊 沙頭角海景靚公屋<br />\n<br />\n今日帶大家來沙頭角禁區，參觀堪稱全港最美公屋。顏色小屋、極低密度，再加上180度無敵環迥大海景！<br />\n<br />\n頭先睇完兩條片都唔夠喉？蘋果VR仲有360片畀你睇！<br />\n電腦用戶可選用Google Chrome瀏覽器，以滑鼠或方向鍵上下左右移動，360&deg;欣賞片段。<br />\n連結：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r9ptd6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r9ptd6&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=339e5392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r9ptd6</a><br />\n<br />\n手機讀者，可率先下載全新《蘋果VR》程式，立即體驗壹傳媒集團旗下製作之所有360&deg;影片及VR互動資訊：<br />\niOS： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/ADVR_iOS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FADVR_iOS&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b33ce3fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/ADVR_iOS</a> <br />\nAndroid： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/ADVR_Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FADVR_Android&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e492b3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/ADVR_Android</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5758En.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5758En.jpg&h=1b623e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56686697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56686697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=657b2cef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56686697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170513&h=0b3f0c51\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56686697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170513</a>"},{"pid":"c7efc308e87c021a4141aaf35ee5fa20c7d0b81d","tid":241134,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"乜鳩私樓控，控你老母咩記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩假期轉職過去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}